I also thank the following for the loan of material that was directly or indirectly involved in generating the present contribution as well as for allowing access to collections: Jerry Harasewych (USNM), Kathie Way (BMNH), Matthias Glaubrecht (ZMB), Ian Loch (AMS), John Stanisic (QM). For numerous improvements on the manuscritpt I am also sincerely grateful to Robert H.
